description: Java class representing a 'Wishlist' entity in the domain model, avec annotations for ORM mapping via JPA. It includes relationships to User and WishlistItem objects and manages wishlist attributes.

classes.name: Wishlist
classes.description: Entity class for wishlists in the application, including fields for id, name, user, creation timestamp, and items, with JPA annotations for persistence.

methods.name: Wishlist(User user, String name)
methods.description: Constructor to create a Wishlist with a specific user and name.

methods.name: getId()
methods.description: Returns the ID of the wishlist.

methods.name: getName()
methods.description: Returns the name of the wishlist.

methods.name: getCreatedAt()
methods.description: Returns the creation timestamp of the wishlist.

methods.name: getItems()
methods.description: Returns the set of WishlistItem objects.

methods.name: setName(String name)
methods.description: Sets the name of the wishlist.
